Package: okschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Oklahoma School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", email = "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Al Martin [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Al Martin <almartin@example.com>
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the Oklahoma State
    Department of Education (OSDE). Provides functions for fetching enrollment
    data from OSDE's public reporting systems and transforming it into tidy
    format for analysis. Supports district and site (school) level enrollment
    data with demographics and grade-level breakdowns.
